---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Services | TechAI Inc">
  <section class="py-6 px-6 md:px-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-800/10 via-violet-900/10 to-black/30 blur-3xl"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="pt-6 pb-16 px-6 md:px-20 text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-10 text-center drop-shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(124,58,237,0.35)]">🌐 Our AI & ML Services</h2>

    <div class="services-grid max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <article id="core-ai-ml" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">🧠 Core AI & Machine Learning</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">Transform data into intelligence. We design, train, and deploy powerful AI and ML models that uncover insights, optimize decisions, and automate complex tasks. From predictive analytics to deep neural networks, our models evolve with your data.</p>
      </article>

      <article id="generative-ai" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">🤖 Generative AI Solutions</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">Create, converse, and innovate with GenAI. We build intelligent chatbots, virtual assistants, and content generators using cutting-edge LLMs. Our RAG-powered systems enable natural Q&A over your enterprise data, transforming customer and employee experiences.</p>
      </article>

      <article id="ai-strategy" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">💡 AI Strategy & Consulting</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">Your roadmap to an AI-driven future. Our experts help you identify high-impact AI opportunities, assess readiness, and build scalable AI strategies. We guide you from proof of concept to full-scale deployment with responsible AI governance.</p>
      </article>

      <article id="data-engineering-mlops" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">⚙️ Data Engineering & MLOps</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">Fuel your AI with clean, connected data. We build robust data pipelines, automate model training, and operationalize ML with CI/CD workflows. Our MLOps frameworks ensure your models stay accurate, efficient, and production-ready�?"always.</p>
      </article>

      <article id="ai-automation-aiops" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">🧩 AI Automation & AIOps</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">Automate smarter, operate faster. We integrate AI with IT operations and business workflows�?"detecting anomalies, predicting failures, and accelerating decisions. With AIOps and LLMOps, we bring intelligence to your DevOps and infrastructure ecosystems.</p>
      </article>

      <article id="conversational-ai" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">💬 Conversational AI & Agents</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">Empower interactions with intelligent chatbots. From customer support to HR automation, our conversational AI systems handle inquiries naturally across web, mobile, and messaging platforms�?"reducing response times and improving satisfaction.</p>
      </article>

      <article id="document-intelligence" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">🧾 Document Intelligence</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">Extract value from your documents. We automate reading, classifying, and summarizing documents using NLP and vision models�?"turning contracts, forms, and invoices into actionable data with unmatched accuracy.</p>
      </article>

      <article id="predictive-analytics" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">📊 Predictive Analytics & Insights</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">See what�?Ts next before it happens. Our predictive and prescriptive analytics reveal hidden trends, optimize business performance, and drive data-backed decisions. We deliver custom dashboards to visualize your KPIs in real time.</p>
      </article>

      <article id="industry-solutions" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">🧭 Industry-Specific AI Solutions</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">Tailored AI for every industry. Whether it�?Ts financial forecasting, medical image analysis, travel route optimization, or manufacturing quality control�?"we deliver domain-specific AI models that deliver measurable impact.</p>
      </article>

      <article id="responsible-ai" class="service-card bg-transparent border border-blue-900/40 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(37,99,235,0.2)]">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">🔐 Responsible & Secure AI</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 mt-1">AI you can trust. We embed transparency, fairness, and compliance into every solution. Our responsible AI frameworks ensure ethical use, data security, and regulatory alignment across all industries.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6 md:px-20 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8">Discuss your use case with our team and explore a pilot tailored to your needs.</p>
      <a href="/contact-us" class="btn-glow inline-block">Talk to Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
